Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Night’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Night” game were:
01-02-05-07-09-10-14-15-20-22-23-24
(one, two, five, seven, nine, ten, fourteen, fifteen, twenty, twenty-two, twenty-three, twenty-four)
